{"tasks":[{"id":39861723,"name":"Architecture/data decisions","description":"**Requirements**\n\n* Determine the following and get green light from Ben on approach\n\n  * Decide on SDK (and which) or FF for limiting tracked users\n\n  * Data mapping for identifiers\n\n  * Data minimization/GDPR compliance\n\n  * Should user email be passed to Amplitude via user properties for debugging?\n\n  * Do we enable autocapture to start?\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":1999,"decimalDisplayOrder":1999,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-12T19:05:37Z","updatedBy":610193,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":490654,"type":"users"},{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:57:55Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":0,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":8660}],"dateUpdated":"2026-03-30T15:28:32Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861097,"name":"Add amplitude snippet to enable tracking","description":"**Requirements**\n\n* We should only implement amplitude tracking on production, and not on demo, qa or staging environments.\n\n* Make sure Amplitude is injected into all authenticated layouts that represent product usage.\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2000,"decimalDisplayOrder":2000,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-14T22:07:41Z","updatedBy":490645,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"},{"id":645330,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:08:37Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":323586,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":2806}],"dateUpdated":"2026-05-14T22:06:46Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[645333,643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861168,"name":"Utilize SDKs to limit what users are tracked in Amplitude","description":"**Background**\n\nIn order to keep our costs down, we cannot afford to track all users in Built.\n\nIf we do not limit the users we are tracking, our annual costs could go from $5k → $50k!\n\nAmplitude mentioned we could utilized their [SDK](https://amplitude.com/docs/sdks?mtl=GafVH1JmYdw)s to limit tracked users.\n\n**Requirements**\n\n* Roles: Only Company Admins, HR Admins, HR Managers, Limited Admins, Recruiting Admins, and Asset Admins\n\n  * We do not want to track users who aren’t assigned an admin role to start.\n\n* Modules/Plans: Only users who belong to companies subscribed to at least one of our modern modules - Org Design, Position Management, Succession Planning, Headcount Planning.\n\n  * We do not want to track users who belong to companies on legacy plans (PTO/TImesheets, Chart/Manage/Plan/Track Your Org)\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2001,"decimalDisplayOrder":2001,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-14T22:07:52Z","updatedBy":490645,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":490654,"type":"users"},{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"},{"id":645330,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":true,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:15:06Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":323586,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":2807}],"dateUpdated":"2026-05-14T22:06:49Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[645333,643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":645333,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861319,"name":"Ensure data minimization/GDPR compliance","description":"**Requirements**\n\nWork with Ben to determine what is needed here.\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2002,"decimalDisplayOrder":2002,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-03-30T15:29:31Z","updatedBy":610193,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:22:54Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":0,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":8657}],"dateUpdated":"2026-03-30T15:28:32Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861252,"name":"Set up tagging for key events  to track","description":"**Requirements**\n\n* Set up targeted tagging so we can track these events in funnels/journeys: [https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17sKlDFvOx-aT-l65m8yL7XMmNZ-D07rVmJMelJz3H9M/edit?gid=0#gid=0](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/17sKlDFvOx-aT-l65m8yL7XMmNZ-D07rVmJMelJz3H9M/edit?gid=0#gid=0)\n\n* Instrumentation must occur on **successful business actions**, not on button click alone. Where possible, emit analytics only after the server confirms persistence. If a client action can fail, the event must not fire on optimistic click alone.\n\n- All event names must:\n\n  * use title case\n\n  * be human-readable\n\n  * describe completed actions\n\n  * avoid synonyms for the same action\n\n  * stay stable once released\n\n- All events must be attributable to a user and a company/account\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2003,"decimalDisplayOrder":2003,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-05-20T20:38:57Z","updatedBy":643631,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":490654,"type":"users"},{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachments":[],"notify":false,"isArchived":false,"capacities":null,"proofs":null,"userPermissions":{"canEdit":true,"canComplete":true,"canLogTime":false,"canViewEstTime":true,"canAddSubtasks":true},"createdBy":610193,"createdAt":"2026-03-17T20:19:26Z","sequence":null,"workflowStages":[{"workflowId":53311,"stageId":323575,"stageTaskDisplayOrder":2267}],"dateUpdated":"2026-05-18T15:18:18Z","parentTaskId":39861084,"tasklistId":2521973,"assigneeUserIds":[643631],"assigneeUsers":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"assigneeCompanyIds":null,"assigneeCompanies":[],"assigneeTeamIds":null,"assigneeTeams":[],"assigneeJobRoleIds":null,"assigneeJobRoles":[],"createdByUserId":610193,"sequenceId":null},{"id":39861555,"name":"Set up properties for events","description":"**Question for dev:** Can we distinguish between impersonation vs true logins by the user?\n\n**Requirements**\n\n* Required global properties on Events\n\n  * Company ID\n\n  * Company Name\n\n  * User\n\n* Object Properties\n\n  * Position events\n\n    * Position ID\n\n    * Source (none, req, hcp)\n\n    * Created from (org chart, positions table, req detail, position panel, hcp datasheet, etc)\n\n    * Connected Budget Period (if present)\n\n    * Connected Budget Source (if present)\n\n  * Requisition events\n\n    * Req ID\n\n    * Source (Req table, position panel, HCP)\n\n  * HCP events\n\n    * HCP ID\n\n    * HCP Status (approved, active)\n\n    * Reqs created from count\n\n    * Positions created from count\n\n  * Budget events\n\n    * Budget Period\n\n    * Budget Source\n\n    * Automatically assigned/manually assigned\n\n* Required User properties. Set/update user properties through identify calls, not by repeating everything on every event unless necessary.\n\n  * Company ID\n\n  * Role\n\n    * Add Ons\n\n      * Budget\n\n  * Plan\n\n    * ID\n\n    * Name\n","descriptionContentType":"TEXT","priority":null,"hasDeskTickets":false,"progress":0,"displayOrder":2004,"decimalDisplayOrder":2004,"crmDealIds":null,"tagIds":null,"tags":null,"updatedAt":"2026-04-30T21:00:18Z","updatedBy":610193,"deletedAt":null,"deletedBy":null,"parentTask":{"id":39861084,"type":"tasks"},"isPrivate":0,"lockdown":null,"status":"new","tasklist":{"id":2521973,"type":"tasklists"},"startDate":null,"dueDate":null,"startDateOffset":null,"dueDateOffset":null,"dueDateBase":null,"dueDateFromMilestone":false,"estimateMinutes":0,"accumulatedEstimatedMinutes":0,"assignees":[{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"commentFollowers":[{"id":610193,"type":"users"},{"id":643631,"type":"users"}],"changeFollowers":[],"completeFollowers":[],"attachme